review: It's great that this app backs up your texts to your email, but the end result is just a mess. It only does sms first, then mms, resulting in messages being out of order and all over the place. Group messaging is a disaster, as the messages get stuck in only one contacts thread, instead of a thread for the group conversation. Expected behavior would be for the app to back up one thread at a time, regardless if mms/sms/etc, and for each thread to be kept together, and in conversation order.
sentence: Group messaging is a disaster, as the messages get stuck in only one contacts thread, instead of a thread for the group conversation.
